withResponse: (NSURLResponse **)  response

[optional]

Optional method that allows the delegate to inject a specific response to a request, which is useful for testing.

Parameters:
manager The sender of the message.
request The request that needs a response.
response This memory location should hold the response to the request, or nil. Should not be a NULL-reference.
error This memory location should hold the error that occured, or nil. Should not be a NULL-reference.
Note:
This method may be called on a thread other than the main thread.
